00:36:48,600 --> 00:36:51,720
So this kind of a mad fasting

546
00:36:51,880 --> 00:36:55,880
is also very bad for your Nabhi and when you do that

547
00:36:56,040 --> 00:36:58,880
then you have a problem because you are invaded

548
00:36:59,040 --> 00:37:04,880
by your left-sided, what you call, beyond

