00:38:02,720 --> 00:38:07,040
and on the right hand side: don't get into indulgences.

564
00:38:07,200 --> 00:38:09,200
Don't pamper yourself.

565
00:38:09,360 --> 00:38:11,680
Both things are the same for Sahaja Yoga.

566
00:38:11,840 --> 00:38:16,240
Whether you starve or you overeat, is the same.

567
00:38:16,400 --> 00:38:18,880
There is no difference between the two,

568
00:38:19,040 --> 00:38:21,640
because if you are not on the seat,

569
00:38:21,800 --> 00:38:22,920
whether you are on the left

570
00:38:23,080 --> 00:38:26,560
falling on the right, does it make any difference?

571
00:38:27,640 --> 00:38:30,960
So to be on the seat is to be

572
00:38:31,160 --> 00:38:33,560
in the blessings of Shri Lakshmi.

