00:38:54,960 --> 00:38:59,360
Imagine. She’s standing on a lotus. That means She is balancing.

578
00:39:00,960 --> 00:39:04,400
And She’s balancing, She’s standing there

579
00:39:04,560 --> 00:39:10,520
and She is holding two lotuses in Her hand showing

580
00:39:11,200 --> 00:39:14,120
that She’s like a lotus.

581
00:39:15,800 --> 00:39:20,440
A person who is a rich man, Lakshmi Pati,

582
00:39:20,600 --> 00:39:25,520
has to be like a lotus, warm, pink, warm.

583
00:39:25,680 --> 00:39:30,320
And even a horrible thing, like

584
00:39:36,320 --> 00:39:39,400
wasp-like thing. I don’t know what you call it in English,

585
00:39:39,480 --> 00:39:41,200
you don’t have that black thing.

586
00:39:41,360 --> 00:39:45,200
We have a very black wasp, you see, which is hard,

587
00:39:45,360 --> 00:39:49,920
hard like nut and has angular thorny legs.

588
00:39:50,080 --> 00:39:54,280
That black thing comes in

