00:40:57,720 --> 00:41:01,680
On the other side are the people

606
00:41:04,360 --> 00:41:11,640
who are so repulsive. They are not like lotus.

607
00:41:11,800 --> 00:41:16,720
There is no fragrance. They are such miserly people

608
00:41:16,880 --> 00:41:21,280
that they stink of miserliness.

